---
title: Smart Rosemary Pork Tenderloin with Apricot-Mustard Vinaigrette, Apples and Sweet Potatoes
description: Tonight's hearty salad with apples and roasted sweet potatoes is dressed in an apricot and mustard vinaigrette and topped with rosemary-coated pork tenderloin.  A sprinkling of crunchy seeds completes a hearty salad that's perfect for any time of the year!
